The '''Ciuray Sea''', known colloquially as the '''Slurry Sea''', was a body of water on the planet [[Metellos/Legends|Metellos]].

==History==
The sea lay close to the [[Moridebo district|Moridebo District]]. It was stagnant and inky gray-brown. Its [[Water/Legends|water]] was processed for drinking by powerful sterilization plants on the shoreline. The sea was a popular dumping ground for unwanted items, including [[Death/Legends|murder]] victims.<ref name="CCW">''[[Coruscant and the Core Worlds]]''</ref>

